data.name: label4.Text
data.value:
This editor lets you edit your server variables, including, but not limited to experience gain from monsters, starting level or amount of money received at character creation.
However if you dont know what you are doing, you can easily break your server. Thus, proceed with caution and only if you KNOW WHAT YOU ARE DOING.
Every server database uses its own configuration file! If server refuses to startup after changing its config, you can revert to the original one using recovery option in menu above.
